Although a little bland, stale, and somewhat corny, this hentai is above average. The doujin itself is nothing novel - many can be found like it. This story follows a somewhat common archetype, one in which the sex is instigated by the MMC being visited by someone he masturbates to. I have no problems with such a format, but it isn't particularly exciting, and nor are the tags under this. The femdom is a little too mild for my tastes, and I don't care for any of the other tags. The art isn't as dynamic as I'd hoped; the FMC's breasts are by far the best feature of this hentai artwise, and seeing as I don't care for those, the art leaves something to be desired for me. The sex scenes are okay, but seem bland as well. The blowjob is boring and the unkinetic sex is carried mostly by the titplay, which is ok, but could be done a lot better. Overall, a 6/10.
